lead_paragraph: A mass protest by fans over ticket prices was not responsible for Liverpool's collapse as they allowed Sunderland to fight back to snatch a 2-2 Premier League draw on Saturday, said assistant coach Pep Lijnders.

headline.print_headline: Liverpool Collapse Nothing to Do With Protest, Says Coach
headline.main: Liverpool Collapse Nothing to Do With Protest, Says Coach
